column2: SELECT Top1#  p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,p.type,   p.isoA_u, p.isoA_g, p.isoA_r, p.isoA_i, p.isoA_z,  p.isoB_u, p.isoB_g, p.isoB_r, p.isoB_i, p.isoB_z,  p.isoPhi_u, p.isoPhi_g, p.isoPhi_r, p.isoPhi_i, p.isoPhi_z FROM PhotoObj AS p WHERE  p.ra BETWEEN %s AND %s  AND p.dec BETWEEN %s AND %s  AND p.type = # ORDER by p.r
